
# Todos-List By React Js 

I created a todos list with basic programmes of react js It is a simple project which is so basic that a react beginner caan understand .



## How To Start This React App

To start this  project in your browser you have to type the command written below :-

```bash
npm start
```
you can run this command and in few minutes your react app get ready 
when your react app get started the terminal look like this.
